00:26:54,921 --> 00:26:57,783
and I was in no way acting alone.

380
00:26:57,866 --> 00:27:00,119
Wilson Fisk coerced me...

381
00:27:02,079 --> 00:27:05,165
My name is Special Agent
Ray Nadeem of the FBI...

